{"tid":472292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛國窮撚好消息, 支那樓市出現逆轉","createTime":"2017-11-18T05:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T11:00:36.000Z","uid":31637,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"55bec78554ab023a49cce5be0c9d9fcfc7df3e78","tid":472292,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T05:54:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1561360190675128/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1561360190675128%2F&d=LokDDrC3299haMjCSi6EvNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=f586707f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1561360190675128/</a><br />\n<br />\n【樓市出現逆轉】<br />\n【學者指中央政策針對瘋漲房價】<br />\n京、津、冀地區及華東地區二、三線城市，樓市出現逆轉。有經濟學者指今次是多年來樓市跌得最急、跌幅最大的一次，主要是中央下了大的決心，以政策針對大陸的瘋漲房價。<br />\n他又指樓市逆轉外，這類地區及城市的共同點是居民儲蓄總額，出現近28年以來首次回落。另外本地銷售總額亦萎縮，地區如天津及蘇州的工業投資，過去幾年全面退潮。<br />\n如果樓市持續下跌，有可能增加銀行壞帳，減少地方政府收入，造成金融危險。<br />\n<br />\n咩人會想樓價跌呀, 咪就係連樓都冇既死窮撚囉屌, 我同你講, 香港最撚窮果班, 非愛國糞青莫屬"},{"pid":"627a90059783bbb47bfa1b8a57bf6dfbd985a04e","tid":472292,"uid":57786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:03:55.000Z","msg":"跌得10%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4dc82625373dc81f01931222450f1b8a047316","tid":472292,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T07:52:36.000Z","msg":"ALL IN係時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07aa53973320c72d2d5ab60d2114d667fc4b195c","tid":472292,"uid":11753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T08:48:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 有經濟學者指今次是多年來樓市跌得最急、跌幅最大的一次，主要是中央下了大的決心，以政策針對大陸的瘋漲房價。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8a86844daf2947dc30ae77bcfdde125a47ff27","tid":472292,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cite